" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Neurofibromata and caf&eacute;-au-lait macules in a patient with neurofibromatosis 1 (NF1)",
